g.text: Understanding SHAP: Individual Player Performance Analysis
How each factor contributes to predicting individual player ratings

SHAP (SHapley Additive exPlanations) shows how each factor contributes to individual player rating predictions. Waterfall plots show single match analysis, while beeswarm plots show patterns across the season.
